      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"flawed argument\"? That's a pretty strong way to put it. Most economic textbooks present the supply-side mechanism as a valid theory, even if it's debated. Why would you categorize the growth argument as \"flawed\" rather than just one perspective in the debate?",
